OL,3,CHospital vandal jailed over
OL,4,CIslamophobic and antisemitic damage
OL,6,FA man who defaced copies of the Quran
OL,7,Fat a hospital and then scrawled
OL,8,Fantisemitic graffiti on his cell wall
OL,9,Ffollowing his arrest has been jailed.
OL,11,FIbrahim Iqbal, 36, smashed a framed
OL,12,Fcopy of Islamic scripture in a multi-
OL,13,Ffaith room at St James's Hospital,
OL,14,FLeeds, last November.
OL,16,FHe tore pages from other copies which
OL,17,Fhe then set alight and stuffed into
OL,18,Fthe sink and toilet.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
