OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773876312
OL,3,CHospital vandal jailed over
OL,4,CIslamophobic and antisemitic damage
OL,6,FIn a second incident 10 days later, he
OL,7,Fcaused further damage in the same room
OL,8,Fand blocked the drains.
OL,10,FIqbal was stopped by security staff
OL,11,Fthe following day when he tried to get
OL,12,Finto the room again and was arrested.
OL,14,FWhile in custody, Iqbal scrawled "kill
OL,15,FJews" on his cell wall at the police
OL,16,Fstation.
OL,18,FThe defendant, of no fixed abode, was
OL,19,Ffound guilty of two counts of
OL,20,Freligiously aggravated criminal damage
OL,21,Fand one count of criminal damage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773876312
OL,3,CHospital vandal jailed over
OL,4,CIslamophobic and antisemitic damage
OL,6,FHe was jailed for 40 weeks.
OL,8,FLeeds district commander Ch Supt Steve
OL,9,FDodds said: "Iqbal caused damage to a
OL,10,Froom in a hospital that is used by
OL,11,Fpeople of all faiths for quiet
OL,12,Freflection and prayer at what can be a
OL,13,Fvery difficult time for them and their
OL,14,Floved ones, ultimately resulting in
OL,15,Fits closure while the damage had to be
OL,16,Frepaired.
OL,26,@qD@MOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
