OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773876312
OL,3,CHospital vandal jailed over
OL,4,CIslamophobic and antisemitic damage
OL,6,F"I know his actions, both at the
OL,7,Fhospital and while in custody, will
OL,8,Fhave been particularly felt within the
OL,9,FMuslim and Jewish communities and I
OL,10,Fhope the police action that has been
OL,11,Ftaken demonstrates that hate crimes
OL,12,Fsuch as this will not be tolerated.
OL,14,F"Everyone has a right to live their
OL,15,Flife, and practice their religion,
OL,16,Fwithout the fear of targeted abuse for
OL,17,Fwho they are."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@NO]
